			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The Emperor has just provided the avatar the option to transform into a mind flayer in order to use the Netherstones to defeat the Netherbrain. Gale has an interest in getting the crown, meaning he needs the stones, so transforming into a mind flayer is probably his best chance to getting it." />
